All a same shit. And now I gatta carry my tired ass to ACME to buy something to eat for my girl, who's closwing store tonight. Alright, folks, see you soon, but now I gatta leave.

You know, it seems to me that such incident as has happend to me this morning can happen only in our country. Ok, get right to the point. Today at 7 a.m. I was woken up by childish voice that was goin' from outside. It was upstairs neighbour's kid was sent to store to buy some stuff.(there is round-the-clock working store in our neighbourhood) Guess that small evel didn't find anything, actually one sort of bread, and came back to ask his mother if he should get another one. But he was in a lazy mood, so he didn't find anything better than scream it out from downstairs. Should say, that his mother is quite well-mannered woman, so she's screamed only one phrase out, but did it loud. She said:" Stop screamin', idiot! All people are sleepin' around." But after that I'm ready  to bet everyone that people around were NOT sleeping anymore. 

Like in "ERALASH", right?

P.S. It's more funny than bad. Anyway, this case cheered me up!! GOOD MORNING, COUNTRY!!!!)
